<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Cancellation and Refund</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      type="text/css"
      href="assets/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container my-5">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Cancellation and Refund Policy</h2>

      <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">
        <h4>Return and Exchange Policy</h4>
        <p>
          Customers can request a cancellation, return, or exchange within
          <strong>7 days</strong> of the purchase date. Requests made beyond
          this period will not be accepted.
        </p>

        <h4>How to Initiate a Return or Exchange</h4>
        <p>
          To request a cancellation, return, or exchange, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: <strong>[Your Email]</strong></li>
          <li>Phone: <strong>[Your Phone Number]</strong></li>
          <li>
            Subject:
            <strong
              >Cancellation/Return Request - Order ID #[Your Order ID]</strong
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Our team will review your request and guide you through the process.
        </p>

        <h4>Refund Processing Time</h4>
        <p>
          Once your return or cancellation is approved, refunds will be
          processed within <strong>7-10 business days</strong>. The amount will
          be credited to the original payment method.
        </p>

        <h4>Non-Refundable Items</h4>
        <p>The following items are non-refundable:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Tickets that have already been used or scanned for entry.</li>
          <li>Transactions made through unauthorized third-party sources.</li>
          <li>Refund requests made after the event date.</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="mt-3">
          <strong
            >By purchasing our services, you agree to our Cancellation and
            Refund Policy.</strong
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
